description: Welcome to 198 Bowen- this stunning NEW CONSTRUCTION 2 bed, 2 bath condo in the heart of South Boston. Thoughtfully designed with modern living in mind, this home boasts a sleek designer kitchen featuring 2 toned cabinetry, Thermador appliances, a massive center island with extra built-in cabinet storage, and a seamless flow into the open concept dining and living space. Gather around the built-in fireplace on chilly winter nights or entertain with ease in the spacious layout. The primary suite offers a custom walk-in closet and a spa-like bath with hand-selected finishes, creating the perfect retreat. A second well-appointed bedroom and full bath with tub complete the home, blending luxury and functionality in one of Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods. 1 GARAGE SPACE included with this unit! This is a unit that you won't want to miss!!
